name: Tezpunks
description:
Tezpunks

Year AD 7702, a group of punks are assigned a mysterious mission. These punks are very deadly. They have their own superpowers. Objectives of the mission will be communicated to them from the command center. For now, the only objective communicated to the punks is to time travel to 2021. 

ID #029


Name         : Drake V7
Strength     : 99/100
Intelligence : 99/100

A robot made by Inpalac labs in the year AD 5835.
Body made with Xelentium, a metal that can even withstand temperatures upto 18000 °C, more than 3 times that of the Sun.
